content: And so you're always going to have timing and I even though as we talk about revenue as we come into the end of the year, we expect to get to $10 million plus, but there's always timing factors that could cause something to slip into the next quarter. If I take the state DOT, that's also a multimillion dollar contract and there's about, roughly $500,000 of revenue in the period that we've contracted for, we're waiting on, but their process won't take delivery until certain signatures are received, and it's a multi-party organization basically.
